Class BigQueryInterface

    • context.core.task.gdelt.BigQueryInterface

  • public class BigQueryInterface
extends java.lang.Object
    Main class for the BigQuery API command line sample. Demonstrates how to make an authenticated API call using OAuth 2 helper classes.
